Summary: RedTurtle Contextual Search Portlet
Home-page: http://plone.org
Author: RedTurtle Technology
Author-email: andrea.cecchi@redturtle.net
License: GPL
Description: Introduction
        ============
        It's an extension of search portlet that allows search for items starting from the current context, and choose whether or not to see the advanced search.
        
